  "identifier": "HB 725",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to a deduction for professional membership dues.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 141.019, relating to income tax, to define terms; allow a deduction from gross income for professional membership dues paid for taxable years beginning on or after January 1, 2027, but before January 1, 2031; amend KRS 131.190 to allow the Department of Revenue to report on the deduction.",
